To build marlin:
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
    make

To install it:
    su
    make install

    or, on sudo based distributions (Ubuntu for instance):
    sudo make install

Options:
    Debug build:
        cmake .. -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
    Other:
        cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DGSETTINGS_COMPILE=OFF -DICON_UPDATE=OFF -DWITH_UNITY=OFF
